articleContent:
Meet Josie (tag #N197​), this week’s Pet of the Week! She is a 9-year-old Labrador retriever mix who is playful, young at heart and loves her rope toys. Josie would prefer to be an only pet and is most comfortable with teenagers and older.
If you are interested in adopting Josie or any other pet, please visit www.SDDAC.com.
